Package: logthis
Title: Structured Logging Framework for R
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "iqis",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "iqis@example.com")
Author: iqis [aut, cre]
Maintainer: iqis <iqis@example.com>
Description: A flexible, structured logging framework for R applications.
    Provides hierarchical event levels, multiple output receivers (console, files, 
    Shiny alerts), configurable filtering, and rich metadata support. Designed 
    for R packages, Shiny applications, and data analysis pipelines requiring 
    enterprise-level logging capabilities.
